{"tid":224824,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咬死男人命根！反性侵「強姦斧」避孕套熱銷","createTime":"2017-05-01T10:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-02T17:39:49.000Z","uid":59565,"like":97,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7637d01ca2828af9e02011468e0ff8ce0c89a3","tid":224824,"uid":59565,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:47:58.000Z","msg":"為了嚇阻性犯罪，南非女醫師葉勒絲(Sonnet Ehlers)在2005年研發一種女性專用的反性侵避孕套「強姦斧」(Rape-aXe)。目前這款產品詢問度愈來愈高，一度造成熱賣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/01/184636_32b72a5fbe5123720e7ac9a0e36789ca.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F01%2F184636_32b72a5fbe5123720e7ac9a0e36789ca.jpg&h=0f621529&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「強姦斧」內有牙齒，可以狠狠咬住性侵者的命根子。(圖／取自網路)<br />\n<br />\n據了解，這款內有「牙齒」的防狼避孕套，內層中空，有鋸齒排列的鉤狀條紋，女性裝在陰道後，如果男性想要性侵，命根子就會被狠狠得「咬死」，只有找求助醫生才能取下，否則只會愈鉤愈緊。<br />\n<br />\n該產品一上市時並沒有受到太多注意，2006年還一度被歐盟要求改名，直到後來陸續有媒體報導，才逐漸受到關注。對於產品一度被外界批評是「保守」，葉勒絲強調，至少要做些事情來反制性侵行為，讓男性在犯罪前能三思而後行。<br />\n<br />\n轉自ETtoday 東森新聞雲<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130209/158454.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20130209%2F158454.htm&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f7e3f7f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20130209/158454.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ada3df9c048296109fc64de0b2ab775a75fcacbb","tid":224824,"uid":59565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"諗下都痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a094c0d85edd5cf2245f0a18912feb763f5a1a2d","tid":224824,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T10:49:33.000Z","msg":"點塞落去？"},{"pid":"98dfbdd04016941d362e004b918ee1a83c9ccb6c","tid":224824,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike