2f256bcba0d5b7efb7748c12f8d838d584","tid":224824,"uid":57800,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:21:59.000Z","msg":"正常強姦會硬左先入，即係條JJ係漲漲地嘅。<br />\n好，咁強行插入受害者私處之後，應該第一下抽插就會畀啲牙咬住。<br />\n本來異常興奮嘅強姦犯會O咗，心諗：做乜鳩？然後會有少許疑惑、最後先識驚。<br />\n即係咁：😧-&gt;🤔-&gt;😨<br />\n成個過程好短，所以強姦者好快就會發現自己JJ出血，而身體亦會即時作出physical嘅回應，簡單啲講即係鳩都縮撚埋。<br />\n由於條JJ已經縮到好似一條毛蟲咁，所以私處內嘅牙唔能夠再咬實佢，強姦者JJ順利拔出。<br />\n但由於血流成河嘅關係，男主角只會訓喺地上扭扭另另喊虎喊忽大叫救命，呢個時候受害者可以選擇趁機逃走，搵黑警幫手拉人；又或者係選擇作出復仇，將自己JJ放返入毫無反擊能力嘅強姦者私處，送出強烈抽插。<br />\n無他嘅，報仇之餘又可以獲得快感，所以話，用左呢個強姦斧避孕套，笑到最後果個一定係你。"},{"pid":"4fabc4ac4a3d57ab7559b381c9ae8d782bb57c6e","tid":224824,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:22:13.000Z","msg":"長期塞住舊野，個西撐到鬆晒"},{"pid":"1b3dfccc537ec4d7144e165ffe42dff3c931b7d4","tid":224824,"uid":101632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:22:16.000Z","msg":"如果個男人係M的話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4fcc86c43b404a418fdc6481d6a5ce2ac892eb","tid":224824,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:22:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小心有牙</blockquote><br />\n而家既連登應該冇咩人明你講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成個連登一定得你識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1d2179e7b9824072360342a4a1705fadcfa3cb9","tid":224824,"uid":40723,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12:25:54.000Z","msg":"帶條即食腸探路"},{"pid":"e07b29a952749ea1536df12ba3231077dfe1475c","tid":224824,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T12